    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Good.",
    "start": 39.36,
    "duration": 2.879
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm feeling very good. I'm just, you",
    "start": 40.399,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "know, getting used to this. It's fun.",
    "start": 42.239,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "My wife's a huge fan of you, by the way.",
    "start": 44.239,
    "duration": 2.961
