    "start": 47.2,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "I love you.",
    "start": 49.12,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I will. Well, I might not, but you",
    "start": 49.92,
    "duration": 2.319
  },
  {
    "text": "know.",
    "start": 52.0,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "What color do you call your beard? Is",
