    "start": 60.719,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "you guys all know, I need to win bad.",
    "start": 62.879,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm feeling good about this. It's time",
    "start": 64.96,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
