    "start": 66.159,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't handle that cockiness. I might",
    "start": 69.52,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "just take him out of the air and even",
    "start": 71.36,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
