    "start": 149.04,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "real bundle of the two. Let's uh let's",
    "start": 150.319,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "take a seat and let Liam and Jeff and",
    "start": 152.0,
    "duration": 3.519
  },
  {
