    "start": 153.599,
    "duration": 3.681
  },
  {
    "text": "moving on to the finale. Next race,",
    "start": 155.519,
    "duration": 3.201
  },
  {
    "text": "Liam, Cory, and Jeff.",
    "start": 157.28,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Feeling pretty good. Can't necessarily",
    "start": 158.72,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "do worse than Kobe.",
    "start": 160.72,
    "duration": 2.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Feeling real good. Feeling real real",
    "start": 161.84,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "good. Not nervous at all.",
    "start": 163.519,
    "duration": 2.481
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, that looks good. You feel",
    "start": 164.72,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "good about that? I I don't even know",
    "start": 166.0,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "what you were doing.",
    "start": 167.28,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Just getting your tasting.",
    "start": 169.12,
    "duration": 4.399
  },
  {
    "text": "I was doing very very good",
    "start": 172.0,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "and bad at the same time.",
    "start": 173.519,
    "duration": 2.321
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, good and bad.",
    "start": 174.72,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "So, I just don't want to do what Kobe",
    "start": 175.84,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "did. I don't want I just want to make a",
    "start": 177.28,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "round one.",
    "start": 179.44,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Three, two, one.",
    "start": 180.16,
    "duration": 4.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh,",
    "start": 185.44,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "speeding so fast right now.",
    "start": 189.76,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Got the tunnel coming up. Oh wow, Liam",
    "start": 192.08,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
