    "start": 194.8,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "way ahead right now, Liam. Way ahead.",
    "start": 197.68,
    "duration": 5.279
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeff is lining up his first obstacle.",
    "start": 200.48,
    "duration": 5.839
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, here comes Liam. Literally half a",
    "start": 202.959,
    "duration": 7.321
  },
  {
