    "start": 206.319,
    "duration": 3.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, go.",
    "start": 212.48,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, he's good. He's good. He pulls up at",
    "start": 214.72,
    "duration": 4.079
  },
  {
