    "start": 226.74,
    "duration": 5.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, he's good. He's good. He's okay.",
    "start": 230.48,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Take your time. I'm telling you. Just",
    "start": 232.56,
    "duration": 4.759
  },
  {
    "text": "take your time.",
    "start": 233.92,
    "duration": 3.399
  },
  {
