    "duration": 2.319
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh my goodness.",
    "start": 240.64,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "How do I get high up?",
    "start": 241.519,
    "duration": 3.761
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay.",
    "start": 242.64,
    "duration": 5.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh no.",
    "start": 245.28,
    "duration": 3.159
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. Goodness. You are being with the",
