    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "victory.",
    "start": 252.879,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Safety is number one priority in all",
    "start": 253.439,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "things. Am I right, Jeff?",
    "start": 256.239,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, sir. I do believe that",
    "start": 257.68,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "in second place.",
    "start": 260.639,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
