    "start": 265.84,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "give Jeff round of applause. Clap it up.",
    "start": 268.0,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, should we make a victory tunnel? A",
    "start": 271.199,
    "duration": 5.401
  },
  {
    "text": "victory tunnel.",
    "start": 273.12,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "That was not a good idea.",
    "start": 278.479,
    "duration": 4.641
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm absolutely elated. That really",
    "start": 280.72,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "apparently he looks like Vincent Van Go",
    "start": 283.12,
    "duration": 3.359
  },
  {
    "text": "and Dale Nhard Jr. combined.",
    "start": 284.88,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, and Michael Rapaort. I said",
    "start": 286.479,
    "duration": 4.641
  },
  {
    "text": "Michael Ravenport to the list.",
    "start": 288.88,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's Dale for a reminder.",
    "start": 291.12,
    "duration": 3.359
  },
  {
