    "start": 293.28,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Liam, who do you look like?",
    "start": 294.479,
    "duration": 3.201
  },
  {
    "text": "I get a few things. You said John John",
    "start": 295.6,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Kazinski.",
    "start": 297.68,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, here he is. He's a real good guy.",
    "start": 298.8,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I like him.",
    "start": 301.44,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "It all comes down to this. In the final",
    "start": 302.08,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "race, we've got three laps. Squaring off",
    "start": 303.68,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Liam, Ty, Cory, and Garrett.",
    "start": 305.68,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "For the finale round, we'll be adding a",
    "start": 310.56,
    "duration": 3.52
  },
  {
