    "start": 314.08,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "the gravity 2000. Four industrial fans",
    "start": 317.44,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "creating updraft, but you got to stay",
    "start": 320.8,
    "duration": 3.679
  },
  {
    "text": "low to get through foggy tunnel.",
    "start": 322.639,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": "Pretty real price on our hands here.",
    "start": 324.479,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "Good competition. Real good competition.",
    "start": 326.56,
    "duration": 6.2
  },
