    "duration": 5.72
  },
  {
    "text": "out of the sky.",
    "start": 392.319,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Holy cow. Oh, is that Liam? Liam's down.",
    "start": 402.16,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "It's Tyler and Garrett.",
    "start": 406.56,
    "duration": 1.759
  },
  {
    "text": "Garrett.",
    "start": 408.08,
    "duration": 3.55
  },
  {
