    "start": 408.319,
    "duration": 8.791
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 411.63,
    "duration": 5.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, here we go.",
    "start": 417.52,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler's the only drone standing. Get",
    "start": 420.0,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "through the tunnel. Okay, he's going",
    "start": 422.4,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "through the smoky tunnel. Straight down",
    "start": 424.0,
    "duration": 3.599
  },
  {
    "text": "the LED lights. How you feel right now?",
    "start": 425.68,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you nervous? This is it, folks.",
    "start": 427.599,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "Victory.",
    "start": 431.28,
    "duration": 2.639
  },
  {
    "text": "I would just like to thank my fans,",
    "start": 432.0,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": "especially my",
    "start": 433.919,
    "duration": 3.481
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 437.73,
    "duration": 4.589
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep. You're doing good. You're doing",
    "start": 441.12,
    "duration": 1.519
  },
  {
    "text": "good.",
    "start": 442.319,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler,",
    "start": 442.639,
    "duration": 2.721
  },
  {
    "text": "yes. On behalf of the entire sports",
    "start": 443.199,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "community, we'd like you to have this.",
    "start": 445.36,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Will you cherish this? Put it somewhere.",
    "start": 447.44,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Absolutely.",
    "start": 449.44,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "It belongs to you and you",
    "start": 449.84,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you. Thank you, Jeff. This one",
    "start": 450.96,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "goes out to all my fans, all my haters",
    "start": 452.24,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "as well. I love you guys. I'm going to",
    "start": 454.16,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "keep killing you with kindness. You",
    "start": 455.68,
    "duration": 2.799
  },
  {
    "text": "know, you can say what you want, but but",
    "start": 457.12,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "I love you guys. So, thank you.",
    "start": 458.479,
    "duration": 3.201
  },
  {
    "text": "Good speech.",
    "start": 459.44,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "That was very moving. What's up, guys?",
    "start": 461.68,
    "duration": 2.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching. Special thanks to",
    "start": 463.36,
    "duration": 2.559
  },
  {
    "text": "our friends at Fox for making this",
    "start": 464.639,
    "duration": 3.361
  },
  {
    "text": "possible, as well as Liam and Jeff. We",
    "start": 465.919,
    "duration": 3.601
  },
  {
    "text": "had an awesome time. If you want to",
    "start": 468.0,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the Independence Day",
    "start": 469.52,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
